<span id="freeTextContainer18404481729185276160"><strong>Murder by love</strong><br/><br/>It started out kind of strange and hard to follow but I kept at it . Being an ex teacher the speech was annoying but I guess people still speak that way in the hills. It was a good story about the trials and temptations of family members living so close together and being somewhat shut off from society they forget the rules. </span>

          </span>
