<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51243325-wilmington-s-lie"><img alt="Wilmington&#39;s Lie: The Murderous Coup of 1898 and the Rise of White Supremacy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1571117991l/51243325._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
